                        <head>No. 613<lb/><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                        <p>On March 11 <persName corresp="#p_BHA1">Byroade</persName> and <persName corresp="#p_HW1">Hallstein</persName> discussed various questions of
                            mutual concern including the Saar. For a record of their conversation,
                            see the memorandum of conversation, <ref target="frus1952-54v07p1#d143">Document 143</ref>.</p>
